{"tid":947093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗衣店貓咪跌進洗衣機慘死 女東主救貓心切左手骨折","createTime":"2018-12-19T04:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T04:38:14.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf09ba7404a864a5ee4b7f7e582d424452a2f65d","tid":947093,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545190340_a9c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545190340_a9c4.jpg&h=1c16a641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545162403_16e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545162403_16e2.jpg&h=5e93aa9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【11:19】涉事洗衣店今早未有營業，女傷者仍留醫<br />\n<br />\n元朗屏會街19號地下一間洗衣店，女東主是愛貓之人，飼養了數隻貓。凌晨零時許，姓鄧57歲女東主開動一部上揭式的洗衣機洗衣服及乾衣，據悉，其中一部洗衣機的滾筒高速轉動為衣物脫水時，疑沒有關上蓋，結果一隻貓疑貪玩或不少心跌入洗衣機內。<br />\n<br />\n女東主見情況危急，救貓心切下伸手入機內救貓無果，反而左手骨折受傷，她其後自行弄停洗衣機後報警。消防員到場將貓隻救出，據悉愛護動物協會人員亦一度到場，惜貓貓被救出後證實已經死亡。救護員到場替受傷女東主包紮後，則把她送屯門醫院救治。"},{"pid":"4a6fe2aef5c40a7b77194b0df00df2e1d16303c3","tid":947093,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf09ba7404a864a5ee4b7f7e582d424452a2f65d","tid":947093,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545190340_a9c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545190340_a9c4.jpg&h=1c16a641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181219/large/1545162403_16e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F1545162403_16e2.jpg&h=5e93aa9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【11:19】涉事洗衣店今早未有營業，女傷者仍留醫<br />\n<br />\n元朗屏會街19號地下一間洗衣店，女東主是愛貓之人，飼養了數隻貓。凌晨零時許，姓鄧57歲女東主開動一部上揭式的洗衣機洗衣服及乾衣，據悉，其中一部洗衣機的滾筒高速轉動為衣物脫水時，疑沒有關上蓋，結果一隻貓疑貪玩或不少心跌入洗衣機內。<br />\n<br />\n女東主見情況危急，救貓心切下伸手入機內救貓無果，反而左手骨折受傷，她其後自行弄停洗衣機後報警。消防員到場將貓隻救出，據悉愛護動物協會人員亦一度到場，惜貓貓被救出後證實已經死亡。救護員到場替受傷女東主包紮後，則把她送屯門醫院救治。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c55f23304936a97df5764ae5c7b40ab88c78ede","tid":947093,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a361b7b74162ff4fbed8f90de4a0ab89157fbb","tid":947093,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2fc595f597a9b5e0cfda5026a222ae491cc86cb","tid":947093,"uid":50253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"d撚屌貓真係好百厭"}]}